Remove log

Put the logs on a file sharing site of some sort- google docs, Dropbox, anything really as long as others can see it and it isn’t riddled with viruses- and put the links to the files in the forums. Without the logs it’ll be nearly impossible to say what went wrong but with the logs it’s usually much easier.
